\cs25\fs16\lang0\langfe1033\langnp0\insrsid15167464\charrsid15167464 1}{\insrsid15167464  If ye then be risen with Christ, seek those things which are above, where Christ sitteth on the right hand of God. }{
\cs25\fs16\lang0\langfe1033\langnp0\insrsid15167464\charrsid15167464 2}{\insrsid15167464  Set your affection on things above, not on things on the earth. }{\cs25\fs16\lang0\langfe1033\langnp0\insrsid15167464\charrsid15167464 3}{\insrsid15167464 
 For ye are dead, and your life is hid with Christ in God.
